ulz4bx"><div dir="auto" data-testid="chatOutput" class="">should i apply for this jobimplementation Project Manager, Hospital Systems 



Compensation: $65.00 - $70.00+ per hour W2 plus benefit and 401k options 

Location: 100% Remote (Eastern or Central Time) – United States
Travel: 20-25% - "as needed" to visit customers and for training/onboarding


Employees: 650 | Team Size: 15 | Revenue: $100M+
Industry: B2B Software, Healthcare, Government | Reports To: Product Line Manager


Responsibilities:

Leading a large-scale enterprise software implementation for a multi-site hospital network
Acting as the “point person” for internal team members and the customer
Project includes hardware installation – including surgical screens, laptops, desktop computers
Overseeing installation and end user training with the support of a large team of SMEs
Managing internal and external stakeholders throughout the project duration
Traveling as needed (domestically) for training, team building, and onboarding for the project (~20-25% max) 


Qualifications:

5+ years of experience in project management with a focus on implementations
Strong background managing software/SaaS projects with hardware components
Strong organizational, leadership, customer-facing, and people management skills
Experience with healthcare (hospital) software projects and/or government (VA) projects
Previous EMR/EHR experience is preferred
PMP Certification highly preferred</div></div></div><i tabindex="0" role="none" data-tabster-dummy="" aria-hidden="true" style="position: fixed; height: 1px; width: 1px; opacity: 0.001; z-index: -1; content-visibility: hidden; top: 0px; left: 0px;"></i></div></div><div class="___1mi8yjl f22iagw fz7g6wx"><div class="___kgn7g00 f22iagw f1vx9l62 fpgzoln fh8aql4 f1wvei1u f6c99af fz7g6wx fly5x3f" data-testid="copilot-message-div"><div class="___19ip04d f1s184ao f6c99af" role="" tabindex="-1" dir="auto" data-testid="copilot-message-reply-div"><i tabindex="0" role="none" data-tabster-dummy="" aria-hidden="true" style="position: fixed; height: 1px; width: 1px; opacity: 0.001; z-index: -1; content-visibility: hidden; top: 0px; left: 0px;"></i><div role="article" tabindex="0" aria-labelledby="copilot-message-rmu-title copilot-message-rmu" data-tabster="{&quot;groupper&quot;:{&quot;tabbability&quot;:2},&quot;focusable&quot;:{}}" aria-busy="true" name="[object Object]" class="fai-CopilotMessage r1f6yzd6 ___1fjo9g7 f1g2tzg5 fgct6un fy77jfu f2c7lf3"><div class="r17kselw"><h6 id="copilot-message-rmu-title" class="fai-CopilotMessage__accessibleHeading rhgro0h">Copilot said: </h6><div class="fai-CopilotMessage__avatar rfv3lde"><div><div class="___13m8sud fq4mcun frvgh55 f1uopt3v fnmerfl" data-testid="messageAttributionIcon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-label="Copilot&#39;s Logo" role="img"><path d="M4.69405 17.2446C5.24991 17.2627 5.50461 17.4556 5.6798 17.688C5.91739 18.0031 6.0556 18.4507 6.24191 19.0835L6.25254 19.1196C6.41716 19.6792 6.63012 20.4032 7.07658 20.9706C7.58358 21.615 8.33343 22.0002 9.4036 22.0002H16.6324C18.1221 22.0002 19.2187 21.0356 20.0072 19.8691C20.8004 18.6957 21.3883 17.1702 21.8439 15.71L21.8455 15.7048C22.3662 14.0356 23.0272 11.9171 23.0027 10.2054C22.9903 9.33711 22.8024 8.4521 22.2166 7.78023C21.6119 7.08669 20.7049 6.75631 19.5545 6.75631H19.3132C18.7574 6.73817 18.5027 6.54526 18.