nl-title user-message-rnl" data-tabster="{&quot;groupper&quot;:{&quot;tabbability&quot;:2},&quot;focusable&quot;:{}}" class="fai-UserMessage rucmimq ___rxrhmb0 fjuset5 f1s184ao fkfq4zb f10kwr27 fmuwq92 f1hyfdyu fjksvth fpgzoln fibxuh5 f6dzj5z"><h5 id="user-message-rnl-title" class="fai-UserMessage__accessibleHeading r183b29h">You said: </h5><button aria-label="More actions" tabindex="-1" class="fai-UserMessage__actionBarAccessibleButton rb330c"></button><div id="user-message-rnl" class="fai-UserMessage__message rulz4bx"><div dir="auto" data-testid="chatOutput" class="">what about this one About FUNDINGO

FUNDINGO is a fast-growing SaaS company revolutionizing alternative lending with the first end-to-end operating system, empowering lenders to scale, streamline operations, and drive growth. Built on Salesforce, our loan management platform transforms fragmented, manual lending processes into a seamless, automated workflow, powering small business, commercial real estate, and community lenders. As a trusted partner in the lending industry, FUNDINGO helps financial institutions unlock efficiency, ensure compliance, and drive revenue growth like never before.


About the Role

As a Project Implementation Specialist, you will play a key role in helping lenders modernize and optimize their operations with FUNDINGO. From post-sale through go-live, you will lead clients through on-boarding, ensuring they maximize the full potential of our platform. This role requires a balance of technical expertise, project management, and client engagement to drive successful implementations. If you're looking to join a high-growth fintech company where innovation meets impact - and where your work directly shapes the future of lending - this is your opportunity to make a difference.


Responsibilities:



Client On-boarding &amp; Implementation

Lead clients through the full implementation lifecycle, including kickoff, requirements gathering, configuration, testing, training, and go-live.
Conduct welcome calls, introduce key team members, and review project scope.
Perform training and walk-throughs of the FUNDINGO loan management platform.
Ask key questions to understand client workflows and identify gaps.


Configuration, Customization &amp; Data Management

Configure and customize FUNDINGO on the Salesforce platform, including building Lightning pages, flows, and fields to meet client needs.
Guide and assist customers through data conversion and migration processes, ensuring seamless transitions.


Project Management &amp; Execution

Oversee project management activities by managing the JIRA board, ensuring tickets are properly prioritized, assigned, and tracked to maintain workflow efficiency and meet deadlines.
Write detailed tickets for the team based on requirements gathered, clearly outlining the requirements, acceptance criteria, and any relevant details to ensure successful implementation.
Provide regular status updates to clients and internal teams.
Manage time logging by recording time spent on projects daily to ensure accurate tracking and reporting.
Monitor project phases, escalate issues when necessary, and ensure alignment on key deliverables.


Process Improvement &amp; Innovation

Identify opportunities for improving implementation processes and system efficiencies.
Contribute to product enhancements by sharing customer insights.
Develop training and configuration documentation to effectively support internal and external stakeholders.


Qualifications:



Technical &amp; Industry Expertise

3-5 years of relevant experience in product implementation, business analysis, consulting, technical support, or technical problem-solving.
2+ years of lending industry experience, with knowledge of loan origination, loan servicing, and alternative lending.
Experience in client services within a B2B/SaaS environment.
Understanding of Salesforce administration, including flows, Lightning page layouts, and reports.


Required Skills:



Project Management &amp; Analytical Skills

Strong problem-solving and critical-thinking skills, with the ability to tailor solutions to customer needs.
Ability to adapt quickly in a fast-paced environment with shifting priorities.
Expertise in breaking down complex processes to ensure clarity, efficiency, and effectiveness.
Ability to envision solutions and understand the process steps from start to finish.
Strong communication and client relations skills, with the ability to ask critical questions and clarify business requirements.</div></div></div><i tabindex="0" role="none" data-tabster-dummy="" aria-hidden="true" style="position: fixed; height: 1px; width: 1px; opacity: 0.001; z-index: -1; content-visibility: hidden; top: 0px; left: 0px;"></i></div></div><div class="___1mi8yjl f22iagw fz7g6wx"><div class="___kgn7g00 f22iagw f1vx9l62 fpgzoln fh8aql4 f1wvei1u f6c99af fz7g6wx fly5x3f" data-testid="copilot-message-div"><div class="___19ip04d f1s184ao f6c99af" role="" tabindex="-1" dir="auto" data-testid="copilot-message-reply-div"><i tabindex="0" role="none" data-tabster-dummy="" aria-hidden="true" style="position: fixed; height: 1px; width: 1px; opacity: 0.001; z-index: -1; content-visibility: hidden; top: 0px; left: 0px;"></i><div role="article" tabindex="0" aria-labelledby="copilot-message-rnp-title copilot-message-rnp" data-tabster="{&quot;groupper&quot;:{&quot;tabbability&quot;:2},&quot;focusable&quot;:{}}" aria-busy="true" name="[object Object]" class="fai-CopilotMessage r1f6yzd6 ___1fjo9g7 f1g2tzg5 fgct6un fy77jfu f2c7lf3"><div class="r17kselw"><h6 id="copilot-message-rnp-title" class="fai-CopilotMessage__accessibleHeading rhgro0h">Copilot said: </h6><div class="fai-CopilotMessage__avatar rfv3lde"><div><div class="___13m8sud fq4mcun frvgh55 f1uopt3v fnmerfl" data-testid="messageAttributionIcon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-label="Copilot&#39;s Logo" role="img"><path d="M4.69405 17.2446C5.24991 17.2627 5.50461 17.4556 5.6798 17.688C5.91739 18.0031 6.0556 18.4507 6.24191 19.0835L6.25254 19.1196C6.41716 19.6792 6.63012 20.4032 7.07658 20.9706C7.58358 21.615 8.33343 22.0002 9.4036 22.0002H16.6324C18.1221 22.0002 19.2187 21.0356 20.0072 19.8691C20.8004 18.6957 21.3883 17.1702 21.8439 15.71L21.8455 15.7048C22.3662 14.0356 23.0272 11.9171 23.0027 10.2054C22.9903 9.33711 22.8024 8.4521 22.2166 7.7802