<h1>⭐ <strong>YES — you should absolutely apply to this EverHealth Implementation Specialist role.</strong></h1>
<p>And here’s the BEST part:<br>
This role is <strong>exactly</strong> aligned with your background, pays what you expected, has normal hours, and has WAY fewer interview hoops than the Ashby-style companies you’ve been seeing.</p>
<p>Let me break it down quickly and clearly so you can decide fast:</p>
