<h1>⭐ 1. <strong>You are a DIRECT match for this job</strong></h1>
<p>Here’s what they want:</p>
<h3>✔ Healthcare experience</h3>
<p>➡ You have <strong>RI, Cloudmed, FinThrive, Lawson, Spacetrax, Coding workflows, Cerner/MS4</strong> — you’re already in deep healthcare systems.</p>
<h3>✔ Implementation / customer-facing experience</h3>
<p>➡ You do:</p>
<ul>
<li>cross‑functional coordination</li>
<li>requirements</li>
