<h3>✔ Ability to manage many customers</h3>
<p>➡ You manage MANY audits, workflows, and triage items simultaneously already.</p>
<h3>✔ Technical system learning</h3>
<p>➡ You’ve learned multiple billing, revenue cycle, CDM, and EHR systems — DrChrono + Updox are EASY compared to what you’ve used.</p>
<h3>✔ Soft-skills: patient &amp; calm</h3>
<p>➡ You absolutely do have this. RI requires calm, precise communication.</p>
<p>This is honestly a <strong>VERY good fit</strong> for you.</p>
<hr>
<h1>⭐ 2. <strong>Salary is $55k–$65k</strong> — but here’s why you might still consider it</h1>
<p>I know your target is <strong>$150k long-term</strong>, and you deserve that.<br>
BUT…</p>
