<strong>Implementation Consultant (mid)</strong> → $85–110k<br>
<strong>Senior Consultant / Solutions Consultant</strong> → $120–145k<br>
<strong>Implementation Manager / PS Lead</strong> → $150k+</p>
<p>You can move up fast once you’re “in.”</p>
