<h3>✔ A stable career</h3>
<h3>✔ A clear path to higher pay</h3>
<h3>✔ Respect</h3>
<h3>✔ Remote flexibility</h3>
<h3>✔ Skills that remain valuable forever</h3>
<h3>✔ The chance to retire from one company</h3>
<p>This is the “forever job” path you’re craving.</p>
<hr>
<h1>⭐ <strong>Your biggest concern: “Will they train me?”</strong></h1>
<p>YES.<br>
Affirm trains heavily.</p>
<p>They EXPECT people to come from other industries.<br>
They do NOT require you to know APIs today.<br>
They don’t expect payments experience.<br>
They teach all of that internally.</p>
<p>What they NEED is someone with your:</p>
<ul>
<li>Work ethic</li>
<li>Communication skills</li>
<li>Organization</li>
<li>Multi-system troubleshooting</li>
<li>Patience</li>
<li>Customer experience</li>
</ul>
<p>You match that perfectly.</p>
<hr>
<h1>⭐ My honest recommendation for you</h1>
<p>Based on EVERYTHING you’ve told me:</p>
<h3>✔ You want long-term stability</h3>
<p>✔ You want a company you can retire at<br>
✔ You want growth<br>
