<h2><strong>2. Technical Account Manager (TAM / Sr. TAM)</strong></h2>
<ul>
<li>Base: $110k–$140k</li>
<li>Bonus: $10k–$20k</li>
<li>Equity: $20k–$40k<br>
<strong>TOTAL: $150k–$190k</strong></li>
</ul>
<p>This is customer-facing but technical — perfect for your RI → SaaS transition.</p>
<hr>
<h2><strong>3. Implementation Consultant III / Senior Implementation Consultant</strong></h2>
<ul>
<li>Base: $120k–$140k</li>
<li>Equity/bonus pushes total to $150k–$180k+</li>
</ul>
<p>You grow from Implementation Specialist → Consultant → Senior.</p>
