<p>Implementation Specialist with 12+ years in regulated industries and 6+ years supporting multi-system workflows, onboarding, data validation, and troubleshooting across complex SaaS-like platforms (Cloudmed, FinThrive, MS4, Cerner, Lawson, Spacetrax). I translate business requirements into clear technical steps, manage UAT and defect triage, coordinate cross-functional teams, and deliver smooth customer implementations. I’m transitioning my strong workflow, QA, and communication background into fintech SaaS implementation with the goal of growing into senior technical or solutions-focused roles.</p>
