phans: 1;"><div class="scriptor-paragraph"><span class="scriptor-textRun scriptor-inline scriptor-nonDisplayable-textRun"># Hi, I'm Leovie 👋</span><br class="scriptor-EOP"></div><div class="scriptor-paragraph"><span class="scriptor-textRun scriptor-inline scriptor-nonDisplayable-textRun"></span><br class="scriptor-EOP"></div><div class="scriptor-paragraph"><span class="scriptor-textRun scriptor-inline scriptor-nonDisplayable-textRun">I'm an Implementation &amp; Systems Analyst transitioning into fintech and SaaS technical implementation.  </span><br class="scriptor-EOP"></div><div class="scriptor-paragraph"><span class="scriptor-textRun scriptor-inline scriptor-nonDisplayable-textRun">I specialize in multi-system troubleshooting, workflow mapping, UAT, data validation, and customer onboarding.</span><br class="scriptor-EOP"></div><div class="scriptor-paragraph"><span class="scriptor-textRun scriptor-inline scriptor-nonDisplayable-textRun"></span><br class="scriptor-EOP"></div><div class="scriptor-paragraph"><span class="scriptor-textRun scriptor-inline scriptor-nonDisplayable-textRun">### 🔧 Core Skills</span><br class="scriptor-EOP"></div><div class="scriptor-paragraph"><span class="scriptor-textRun scriptor-inline scriptor-nonDisplayable-textRun">- SaaS implementation &amp; onboarding</span><br class="scriptor-EOP"></div><div class="scriptor-paragraph"><span class="scriptor-textRun scriptor-inline scriptor-nonDisplayable-textRun">- Cross-system integrations (Cloudmed/R1, FinThrive, MS4/Cerner, Lawson, Spacetrax)</span><br class="scriptor-EOP"></div><div class="scriptor-paragraph"><span class="scriptor-textRun scriptor-inline scriptor-nonDisplayable-textRun">- Requirements gathering &amp; acceptance criteria</span><br class="scriptor-EOP"></div><div class="scriptor-paragraph"><span class="scriptor-textRun scriptor-inline scriptor-nonDisplayable-textRun">- UAT scripts, defect triage, and validation evidence</span><br class="scriptor-EOP"></div><div class="scriptor-paragraph"><span class="scriptor-textRun scriptor-inline scriptor-nonDisplayable-textRun">- SQL (basic), Python (beginner), JSON, API concepts</span><br class="scriptor-EOP"></div><div class="scriptor-paragraph"><span class="scriptor-textRun scriptor-inline scriptor-nonDisplayable-textRun">- Workflow documentation, process diagrams, job aids</span><br class="scriptor-EOP"></div><div class="scriptor-paragraph"><span class="scriptor-textRun scriptor-inline scriptor-nonDisplayable-textRun">- Excel (advanced), Smartsheet, ServiceNow, JIRA, Confluence</span><br class="scriptor-EOP"></div><div class="scriptor-paragraph"><span class="scriptor-textRun scriptor-inline scriptor-nonDisplayable-textRun"></span><br class="scriptor-EOP"></div><div class="scriptor-paragraph"><span class="scriptor-textRun scriptor-inline scriptor-nonDisplayable-textRun">### 📁 Featured Repositories</span><br class="scriptor-EOP"></div><div class="scriptor-paragraph"><span class="scriptor-textRun scriptor-inline scriptor-nonDisplayable-textRun">- </span><span class="scriptor-textRun scriptor-inline codeBlock-token-bold">**</span><span class="scriptor-textRun scriptor-inline codeBlock-token-bold">cdm-validator-python</span><span class="scriptor-textRun scriptor-inline codeBlock-token-bold">**</span><span class="scriptor-textRun scriptor-inline"> – Python logic for validating charge data rules  </span><br class="scriptor-EOP"></div><div class="scriptor-paragraph"><span class="scriptor-textRun scriptor-inline scriptor-nonDisplayable-textRun">- </span><span class="scriptor-textRun scriptor-inline codeBlock-token-bold">**</span><span class="scriptor-textRun scriptor-inline codeBlock-token-bold">sql-tableau-portfolio</span><span class="scriptor-textRun scriptor-inline codeBlock-token-bold">**</span><span class="scriptor-textRun scriptor-inline"> – SQL samples + Tableau visuals  </span><br class="scriptor-EOP"></div><div class="scriptor-paragraph"><span class="scriptor-textRun scriptor-inline scriptor-nonDisp